HEADWORD: loose-fitting
<hw>loose-fitting</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>large enough to leave space
for movement over the skin; not tight-fitting; -- of clothing. Opposite
of <ant>close-fitting</ant>, <ant>tight</ant>, and
<ant>tight-fitting</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> loose.</syn>⟦br⟧
